textBody:
Anastasius I or Anastasios I may refer to:
*Anastasius I Dicorus (b. 430 –  518), Roman Emperor
*Anastasius I of Antioch (d. 599), Patriarch of Antioch
*Pope Anastasius I (died 401), Pope of Rome
